{
  "id": "69b088ae25d09790a9667d64",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:要件定義",
  "created": 1773177141,
  "updated": 1773579073,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b088ae25d09790a9667d64",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:要件定義",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177141,
      "updated": 1773177141
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08934000000000047dba4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177141,
      "updated": 1773579001
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dba6",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dba7",
      "text": "はいどーも！今日のゆるっと鼎談タイム〜。テーマはズバリ「[要件定義]」！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773578996
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dba8",
      "text": "……って言うとなんか難しそうだけど、ざっくり言うと「作る前に“何を作るかちゃんと決めとこね”っていう話」ってやつだよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dba9",
      "text": "ゲーム開発でもよく聞くやつ。これミスると開発が地獄モード突入ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbaa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbab",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbac",
      "text": "（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbad",
      "text": "確かに、ものごとの始まりを整える作業なのですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbae",
      "text": "物語を書くときにも、似たようなものを感じます。登場人物がどのような願いを抱き、どこへ向かうのか――それを最初に思い描かなければ、物語は霧の中をさまようようになってしまいますから。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbaf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbb0",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbb1",
      "text": "概ね正しい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbb2",
      "text": "ソフトウェア工学では、要件定義はRequirements Definitionと呼ばれる工程。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbb3",
      "text": "目的は主に3つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbb4",
      "text": " 1. システムの目的を明確化する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbb5",
      "text": " 2. ユーザーが必要としている機能を整理する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbb6",
      "text": " 3. 開発チームと依頼者の認識を一致させる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbb7",
      "text": "ここが曖昧だと、後工程の設計・実装が破綻する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbb8",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbb9",
      "text": "https://www.atlassian.com/agile/project-management/requirements",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbbb",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbbc",
      "text": "おお、りかさん今日も安定のガチ勢。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbbd",
      "text": "でもさー、要件定義って[** 「お客さんが本当に欲しいもの」問題]あるよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbbe",
      "text": "「こういうシステム欲しい！」って言われて作ったら",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbbf",
      "text": "「思ってたのと違う…」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbc0",
      "text": "ってなるやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbc1",
      "text": "それ一番ダメなやつｗｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbc2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbc3",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbc4",
      "text": "よくある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbc5",
      "text": "理由はシンプル。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbc6",
      "text": "依頼者は[** 「解決したい問題」ではなく「思いついた解決方法」を言うことが多い]。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbc7",
      "text": "例：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbc8",
      "text": "依頼者",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbc9",
      "text": " 「Excelを自動化するツールが欲しい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbca",
      "text": "実際の問題",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbcb",
      "text": " 「毎日の集計作業が大変」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbcc",
      "text": "この場合、解決策は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbcd",
      "text": " 集計の自動化",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbce",
      "text": " データ入力の改善",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbcf",
      "text": " システム化",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbd0",
      "text": "など複数あり得る。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbd1",
      "text": "つまり、問題の本質を抽出する工程が要件定義。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbd2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbd3",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbd4",
      "text": "それは、人の願いを丁寧に聞き取る作業なのですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbd5",
      "text": "言葉というものは、ときに心の表面をなぞるだけで、奥にある思いまでは映しません。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbd6",
      "text": "ですから、「どうしてそれを望まれるのですか」と、静かに問いかけていくことが大切なのでしょう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbd7",
      "text": "まるで、物語の人物の胸の内をそっと探るように。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbd8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbd9",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbda",
      "text": "あや姉、表現が完全に文学ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbdb",
      "text": "でもマジでそれある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbdc",
      "text": "「なんでそれ欲しいの？」を5回くらい聞くやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbdd",
      "text": "確か[** 「[なぜなぜ分析]」]とかって呼ばれてるんだっけ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773579030
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbde",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbdf",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbe0",
      "text": "その通り。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbe1",
      "text": "なぜなぜ分析（5 Whys）。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbe2",
      "text": "トヨタ生産方式で有名な問題分析手法。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbe3",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Five_whys",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbe4",
      "text": "例：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbe5",
      "text": " 1. なぜ集計が大変？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbe6",
      "text": "  → 手作業だから",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbe7",
      "text": " 2. なぜ手作業？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbe8",
      "text": "  → システム連携がない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbe9",
      "text": " 3. なぜ連携がない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbea",
      "text": "  → 古いシステムだから",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbeb",
      "text": "ここまで掘ると、本当の要件が見えてくる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbec",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbed",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbee",
      "text": "なるほどねー。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbef",
      "text": "つまり要件定義って",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbf0",
      "text": " 欲しいものを聞く",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbf1",
      "text": " 本当に困ってることを探す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbf2",
      "text": " みんなで認識合わせする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbf3",
      "text": "っていう超重要な下準備って感じか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbf4",
      "text": "RPGで言うと最初のクエスト説明だね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbf5",
      "text": "ここ聞き逃すと",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbf6",
      "text": "「え、ドラゴン倒すんじゃなかったの！？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbf7",
      "text": "みたいになる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbf8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbf9",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbfa",
      "text": "（笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbfb",
      "text": "それは、たいへんな冒険になってしまいますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbfc",
      "text": "けれど、準備を整えるというのは、少しだけ勇気のいることかもしれません。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbfd",
      "text": "人はつい、早く作り始めたくなってしまうものですから。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbfe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dbff",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc00",
      "text": "それは事実。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc01",
      "text": "多くのプロジェクトが失敗する理由の一つは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc02",
      "text": "「急いで作り始めること」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc03",
      "text": "研究でも指摘されている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc04",
      "text": "（Standish Group CHAOS Report）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc05",
      "text": "https://www.standishgroup.com/chaos-reports",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc06",
      "text": "失敗要因の上位は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc07",
      "text": " 要件の不明確さ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc08",
      "text": " 要件変更",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc09",
      "text": " 利害関係者の認識ズレ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc0a",
      "text": "全部、要件定義に関係している。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc0b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc0c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc0d",
      "text": "うわー、つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc0e",
      "text": "要件定義サボる → 開発大炎上",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc0f",
      "text": "ってことか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc10",
      "text": "バグより怖いじゃんそれ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc11",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc12",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc13",
      "text": "正確には",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc14",
      "text": "要件のバグ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc15",
      "text": "コードのバグより修正コストが高い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc16",
      "text": "ソフトウェア工学では",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc17",
      "text": "後工程ほど修正コストが増える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc18",
      "text": "という原則がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc19",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc1a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc1b",
      "text": "うわそれ聞いたことある！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc1c",
      "text": "バグ直すコスト",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc1d",
      "text": " 要件 → 1",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc1e",
      "text": " 設計 → 10",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc1f",
      "text": " 実装 → 100",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc20",
      "text": "みたいなやつだっけ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc21",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc22",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc23",
      "text": "近い概念。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc24",
      "text": "「1:10:100ルール」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc25",
      "text": "だから、要件定義は地味だけど最重要工程。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc26",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc27",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc28",
      "text": "（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc29",
      "text": "なるほど……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc2a",
      "text": "それは、家を建てる前に地図を広げて、どこに窓を開けるか、どこに庭をつくるかを思い描くようなものですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc2b",
      "text": "急いで柱を立ててしまえば、あとから景色を変えることは難しくなってしまう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc2c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc2d",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc2e",
      "text": "あや姉の例え分かりやすい！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc2f",
      "text": "じゃあまとめるね〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc30",
      "text": "今日のふーこ的まとめ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc31",
      "text": "要件定義とは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc32",
      "text": "　何を作るか決める",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc33",
      "text": "　本当に解決したい問題を見つける",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc34",
      "text": "　関係者みんなで「これ作るね！」って合意する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc35",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc36",
      "text": "[** 「開発の地図づくり」」]って感じ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc37",
      "text": "これミスると",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc38",
      "text": "プロジェクト迷子＼(^o^)／",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc39",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc3a",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc3b",
      "text": "的確な要約。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc3c",
      "text": "要件定義は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc3d",
      "text": "プロジェクトの運命を決める儀式。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc3e",
      "text": "軽視すると、システムは混沌に飲まれる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc3f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc40",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc41",
      "text": "（静かに笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc42",
      "text": "けれど、丁寧に耳を傾ければ、きっとよい道筋が見えてくるのでしょうね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc43",
      "text": "人の願いを形にするというのは、どこか物語を書くことにも似ていて――",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc44",
      "text": "少しだけ、素敵なお仕事のように思えてきました。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc45",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc46",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc47",
      "text": "それな！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc48",
      "text": "じゃあ次回テーマどうする？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc49",
      "text": "[** 「仕様変更あるある」]とか？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc4a",
      "text": "絶対カオス回になるやつｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc4b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc4c",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc4d",
      "text": "……予感しかしない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc4e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc4f",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc50",
      "text": "（笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc51",
      "text": "それもまた、物語の波乱のようで楽しそうですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08935000000000047dc52",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177142,
      "updated": 1773177142
    },
    {
      "id": "69b6ab3b000000000044abf7",
      "text": "[ゆるトーク:仕様変更あるある]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773579068,
      "updated": 1773579073
    },
    {
      "id": "69b6ab3d000000000044abf8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773579070,
      "updated": 1773579070
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08938000000000047dc53",
      "text": "#2026-03-11",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177144,
      "updated": 1773177154
    },
    {
      "id": "69b08939000000000047dc54",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773177145,
      "updated": 1773177145
    }
  ]
}